Detailed Description

template<typename KEY, typename VALUE, typename TRAITS>
struct cds::ordered_list::OrderedList< KEY, VALUE, TRAITS >

Base of ordered list classes.

Template parameters
  • KEY type of key stored in list
  • VALUE type of value stored in list
  • TRAITS list traits. If TRAITS == void then default implementation cds::ordered_list::type_traits is selected.
All ordered list is derived from this class. In turn, this class derived from ordered_list_tag class.
